@{bg shine}Transparent@{bg background}

Draws only the border of the hand.

@{bg shine}Fit To Nums@{bg background}

Fits the hand directly to the dail.
Its only useable for non-circle dails (Rectangle).

@{bg shine}FillColor...@{bg background}

Sets the color that fills the hand. Transparents has to be turned off.

@{bg shine}BorderColor...@{bg background}

Sets the color for the handborder.

@{bg shine}Shadow@{bg background}

Turns the shadow for the hourhand on/off.

@{bg shine}Shadow Depth...@{bg background}

Sets the shadowdepth for the shadow of the minutehand.
@ENDNODE

